## File Layout Rules
- Screens: `src/features/[feature]/[name]-screen.tsx`
- Routes: `src/app/` — file name becomes the URL path (Expo Router)
- API calls: `src/lib/api/driver/` — one file per resource type
- Types: `src/lib/types.ts` — keep in sync with adtruck-proof-main
- Always use `@/` absolute imports — never `../` relative imports
- Never edit `android/` or `ios/` directories directly — use Expo config plugins

