## Auth Rules
- Session tokens are stored in MMKV via the custom adapter in `src/lib/supabase.ts`
- Do NOT switch to AsyncStorage or expo-secure-store (secure-store has a 2048-byte size limit that breaks Supabase JWTs)
- Login flow: username → RPC `get_auth_email_by_username` → `signInWithPassword`
- Auth state lives in `src/features/auth/use-auth-store.tsx` (Zustand store)
- Never log JWTs, session tokens, refresh tokens, or passwords — even behind `__DEV__`
- `hydrateAuth()` is called at module scope in `src/app/_layout.tsx` — do not move it

