## Test Rules — IMPORTANT: existing tests have known issues

The file `src/features/auth/components/login-form.test.tsx` uses:
- testID `email-input` — WRONG (actual component uses `username-input`)
- text "Email is required" — WRONG (actual error is "Username is required")
- field name `email` in submit assertion — WRONG (actual field is `username`)

**Do not copy patterns from this test file.** All 3 non-trivial tests in it will fail.
Fix this file before adding new tests — update testIDs and error strings to match the component.

General test rules:
- testIDs in component and test file must match exactly
- Never hit real Supabase in Jest — mock `@/lib/supabase`
- Test what the user sees and does — not internal implementation details

