## What Not To Do
- **No OTP login** — project rule, non-negotiable
- **No AsyncStorage** — use MMKV
- **No react-hook-form** — use TanStack Form
- **No `git add .`** — stage specific files only
- **No `.env` commits**
- **Do not modify the MMKV adapter in `supabase.ts`** without reading the 2048-byte comment in that file first
- **Do not use v2/v3 date-fns tokens** — this project is on v1.30.1
